### Service metadata (to verify service is up and endpoints exist)
GET {{baseUrl}}/catalog/$metadata

### Read Students (list all)
GET {{baseUrl}}/catalog/Students HTTP/1.1

### Create Student
POST {{baseUrl}}/catalog/Students HTTP/1.1
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "firstName": "John",
  "lastName": "Wayne",
  "email": "john.wayne@example.com",
  "age": 21
}

### Update Student (change age)
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/catalog/Students(ID='{{UUID}}') HTTP/1.1
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "age": 22
}

### Delete Student
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/catalog/Students(ID='{{UUID}}') HTTP/1.1

### Read Books (entity read — optional verification)
